How is this possible?

563
00:38:04,160 --> 00:38:05,480
If you are in the Yamen of the state capital

564
00:38:05,920 --> 00:38:07,160
Of course he refused

565
00:38:07,360 --> 00:38:09,600
But if it is in front of the people of Tanxi Town,

566
00:38:09,680 --> 00:38:11,200
in full view

567
00:38:11,520 --> 00:38:13,440
Put the evidence in front of him one by one

568
00:38:13,920 --> 00:38:15,520
I can't tolerate him denying it

569
00:38:16,600 --> 00:38:17,440
you mean

570
00:38:18,280 --> 00:38:19,240
Suwen Conference?

571
00:38:19,520 --> 00:38:20,640
I don't agree

572
00:38:21,680 --> 00:38:23,960
How many years has it been since Bai Yutang’s medical skills were abandoned?

573
00:38:24,040 --> 00:38:25,680
He is just a layman now

574
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:27,600
How can I participate in the Suwen Conference?

575
00:38:28,120 --> 00:38:31,160
After all, Xiao Qi is a descendant of my Jin family.

576
00:38:31,240 --> 00:38:33,440
His brother is his brother, he is him

577
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:34,800
Don't let him come

578
00:38:35,200 --> 00:38:36,400
Unreasonable

579
00:38:38,600 --> 00:38:39,520
fifth uncle

580
00:38:40,080 --> 00:38:41,600
The fourth aunt is newly deceased

581
00:38:41,680 --> 00:38:43,480
The whole house is sad and depressed

582
00:38:43,880 --> 00:38:45,120
Su Wen Conference

583
00:38:45,200 --> 00:38:46,400
Can it be postponed?

584
00:38:47,520 --> 00:38:50,160
The Suwen Conference has never been interrupted for a hundred years.

585
00:38:50,480 --> 00:38:52,760
Not to mention why weddings and funerals are rescheduled

586
00:38:53,280 --> 00:38:54,480
You tell me first

587
00:38:54,560 --> 00:38:56,520
Why did Tang Ji kill people in the mourning hall?

588
00:38:56,880 --> 00:38:58,000
You and this Tang Clan

589
00:38:58,400 --> 00:38:59,920
Is there any connection?

590
00:39:00,800 --> 00:39:01,760
fifth uncle

591
00:39:02,160 --> 00:39:04,360
The most important thing right now is the Suwen Conference

592
00:39:06,120 --> 00:39:07,760
Don't blame me for not reminding you

593
00:39:07,840 --> 00:39:09,200
Xiao Qi’s thoughts

594
00:39:09,280 --> 00:39:11,120
It’s not about competing in medical skills at all.

595
00:39:11,200 --> 00:39:13,880
He was trying to help his dead brother overturn the case.

596
00:39:14,080 --> 00:39:16,160
It would be a good thing if he could really do it

597
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:18,400
Can clear the name of my Jin family

598
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:19,680
Why did you stop him?

599
00:39:20,920 --> 00:39:22,640
It’s not that I have to collude with the Tang Clan

600
00:39:22,720 --> 00:39:23,880
It's because of the fourth aunt...

601
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:33,960
fifth uncle

602
00:39:35,960 --> 00:39:37,960
Let me simply tell you the truth.

603
00:39:38,800 --> 00:39:40,320
If Bai Yutang reverses the verdict

604
00:39:41,200 --> 00:39:42,320
Then our Jin family

605
00:39:43,320 --> 00:39:45,760
Another scandal must be exposed

606
00:39:52,080 --> 00:39:53,040
Report of trouble

607
00:39:53,120 --> 00:39:54,280
Tanxi Town Jinfu

608
00:39:54,360 --> 00:39:57,160
I sincerely invite Zhizhou to come and watch the Suwen Conference tomorrow.

609
00:39:57,240 --> 00:39:58,080
Not going…

610
00:39:58,160 --> 00:39:59,200
My Zhizhou said

611
00:39:59,280 --> 00:40:01,320
I've been busy with work lately and haven't had time to attend the ceremony.

612
00:40:05,240 --> 00:40:06,240
Then forget it

613
00:40:06,840 --> 00:40:08,800
Don't blame us for not reminding you then.

614
00:40:09,240 --> 00:40:11,720
This noble man from Tokyo came to the conference in person

615
00:40:11,800 --> 00:40:13,120
Knowing the state but not showing favor

616
00:40:13,400 --> 00:40:15,360
I'm just afraid I'll offend someone

617
00:40:16,160 --> 00:40:17,400
A Tokyo nobleman?

618
00:40:17,760 --> 00:40:18,680
yes

619
00:40:18,760 --> 00:40:20,800
The noble man traveled far and wide and passed by Xiangyang

620
00:40:20,880 --> 00:40:22,480
I heard about this great event

621
00:40:22,560 --> 00:40:23,960
Rarely interested

622
00:40:24,040 --> 00:40:25,280
I still want to watch the excitement

623
00:40:25,640 --> 00:40:26,560
-Forget it, let's go. -Let's go.

624
00:40:28,120 --> 00:40:29,120
You two stay behind

625
00:40:29,200 --> 00:40:31,520
Which noble person in Tokyo are you talking about?

626
00:40:38,360 --> 00:40:39,800
Is everything you said true?

627
00:40:40,120 --> 00:40:41,080
Have you verified it?

628
00:40:41,160 --> 00:40:44,000
The fourth aunt admitted it herself, there will be no lies.

629
00:40:45,640 --> 00:40:48,280
Why do you think Tang Ji went on a killing spree at the funeral?

630
00:40:48,520 --> 00:40:49,720
It's because of Bai Yutang

631
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:51,600
Coercing the fourth aunt to go to court

632
00:40:52,520 --> 00:40:54,240
It was Bai Yutang who forced her to death

633
00:40:56,280 --> 00:40:57,320
fourth aunt

634
00:40:58,040 --> 00:41:00,040
Protect the reputation of our Jin family

635
00:41:00,120 --> 00:41:01,800
Saved the face of the children

636
00:41:02,160 --> 00:41:04,160
To prove that Jiulang has been to Feihua'ao

637
00:41:04,240 --> 00:41:06,120
Their affair will definitely be exposed

638
00:41:06,440 --> 00:41:07,920
Cleared a stigma

639
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:10,000
Another scandal was revealed

640
00:41:10,080 --> 00:41:11,680
This is for our Jin family

641
00:41:12,320 --> 00:41:13,800
no benefit

642
00:41:16,080 --> 00:41:17,000
fifth uncle

643
00:41:17,200 --> 00:41:18,680
It's better to keep silent

644
00:41:19,040 --> 00:41:20,840
It's an old case anyway

645
00:41:20,920 --> 00:41:21,840
maybe

646
00:41:22,720 --> 00:41:24,320
Not many people will remember

647
00:41:37,440 --> 00:41:38,560
Kuro

648
00:41:40,040 --> 00:41:41,840
If you are really wronged

649
00:41:44,440 --> 00:41:45,360
That…

650
00:41:48,280 --> 00:41:49,120
Head of house

651
00:41:51,760 --> 00:41:52,640
old patriarch

652
00:41:52,720 --> 00:41:53,720
There's someone outside asking to see you

653
00:41:53,800 --> 00:41:55,640
A person who claims to be in charge of the palace

654
00:41:55,920 --> 00:41:56,920
The palace?

655
00:41:58,560 --> 00:42:00,640
Please come soon...

656
00:42:11,720 --> 00:42:12,600
old patriarch

657
00:42:12,680 --> 00:42:14,480
My surname is Zhao, Zhao Zhier

658
00:42:14,560 --> 00:42:16,360
He was the steward of King Hui of the Nanqing Palace

659
00:42:49,080 --> 00:42:50,600
The oral message of the prince

660
00:42:50,680 --> 00:42:52,160
This year’s Suwen Conference

661
00:42:52,240 --> 00:42:53,480
The prince will come to watch the ceremony

662
00:42:54,320 --> 00:42:55,560
King Hui is coming?

663
00:42:55,640 --> 00:42:58,760
Yes, my prince was invited by his good friend Bai Yutang

664
00:42:58,840 --> 00:43:01,040
I came here especially to watch him and all the Xinglin masters

665
00:43:01,120 --> 00:43:02,480
Discuss medical skills and pharmacy

666
00:43:02,560 --> 00:43:04,200
King Hui came to watch the ceremony

667
00:43:04,280 --> 00:43:06,280
It really makes the humble house shine brightly
